  "description": "This repository contains all supplementary materials associated with the manuscript \u201cFerroptosis\u2013Inflammation Gene Signature Reveals Diagnostic Biomarkers and Immune Subtypes in Sepsis-Induced Cardiomyopathy\u201d. The files include supplementary figures and tables supporting transcriptomic analyses, diagnostic model construction, immune infiltration profiling, and experimental validation.",
